In general, most of the @dfn{STREAMS} utility functions that were present in @cite{SVR 3.2} also
made it into @cite{SVR 4} (with few exceptions).  @cite{SVR 3.2} did not yet have the concept of a
DDI/DKI, but the @dfn{STREAMS} functions present in @cite{SVR 3.2} appear in the @cite{SVR 4.2 MP}
